desc: Sande Gene designs Timeless, sustainable custom handcraft jewelry from re-purposed, recycled materials, uniquely made for you. Our beautiful heritage jewelry deserves to be reclaimed into one-of-a-kind heirloom pieces. Jewelry Making classes teaching these unique techniques & tips. Contact us for more information.

SANDE GENE DESIGNS AND CREATES
